news.title: Ludhiana civic body seals six hotels for illegal construction
news.para: Among these are Hotel Friends Regency, Hotel Nagpal Regency, Hotel Onn, Hotel Silver Stone, Hotel Diamond and Hotel Surya Regency.

news.title: Gurugram: DLF 1 residents complain about inadequate social infrastructure
news.para: Savita Choudhary, another resident of DLF-1, said, "Water is the major issue in our ward because there is a gap between demand and supply.

news.title: ADB approves $200 million loan to enhance urban infrastructure in Kolkata
news.para: These interventions, which are part of the Kolkata Municipal Corporation Sustainability, Hygiene, and Resilience (Sector) Project, will improve the living conditions and health outcomes, particularly for vulnerable groups including women and children.

news.title: Allahabad HC seeks unauthorized construction details from Uttar Pradesh government, LDA
news.para: The order was passed by the bench of justices AR Masoodi and Manish Kumar on the public interest litigation filed in 2012 by Lieutenant Colonel (retired) Ashok Kumar.

news.title: Kalyan-Dombivli civic body files case against five developers for illegal construction
news.para: The case was registered against developers Kitabullah Sheikh, Baitullah Sheikh, Mukhlish Kabadi, Iftikhar Kabadi, and Zulfiqar Khaliq.

news.title: Purple Style Labs leases 59,000 sq ft commercial space in South Mumbai’s Fort
news.para: The 110-year-old property at Flora Fountain was previously leased to Spanish retailer Zara that shut the store earlier this month after nearly eight years of operations.

news.title: Holcim moves closer to spin-off its North American business after SEC filing
news.para: Holcim has made a filing to the United States securities regulator about the divestment to shareholders, likely to be one of the biggest deals in the global construction market this year.

news.title: Private home prices in Hong Kong fell 0.4% in January 2025
news.para: Private home prices fell 0.4% in January from the month before, following a revised 0.9% decline in December, data from the Rating and Valuation Department showed.

news.title: Germany: Allianz real estate portfolio drops 7.7% in 2024
news.para: The German insurer's real estate portfolio dropped 7.7% last year to 53.9 billion euros, coming on top of a 6.2% drop the previous year.

news.title: Hrithik Roshan lease out 9,209 sq ft office space in Pune
news.para: The property spread over 9,209 sq ft on the 8th floor of the World Trade Centre has been let out at monthly rentals of Rs 6.08 lakh sq ft, showed the documents accessed through CRE Matrix, a real estate data analytics firm.

news.title: Hedge funds bet big on China property stocks' recovery
news.para: Investors said recent positive signs, from improving home prices in top cities to industry leader China Vanke's recapitalization plan, suggest this year will be the turning point for the real estate market.

news.title: US: CFPB dismisses lawsuit against Berkshire Hathaway's unit over risky home loans
news.para: The CFPB on Thursday also dismissed multiple other lawsuits, including a case against Capital One. Its dismissals have been with prejudice, meaning the agency cannot pursue the cases again.

news.title: Kerala government not to amend land pooling rules
news.para: Earlier, GCDA, which was appointed the agency for pooling land, had approached state govt demanding amendments to land pooling rules notified by govt.

news.title: Meerut civic body seals 56 shops over unpaid house taxes
news.para: Chief tax assessment officer SK Gautam said that in Kotla Bazaar and Swamipada, Rs 9.20 crore was outstanding, leading to the seizure of 20 shops, with Rs 1.63 lakh recovered.

news.title: Goa: HC reserves verdict on pleas against TCP Act provision to ‘correct’ zones
news.para: ​​The previous division bench of the HC heard the case for around two months, but before hearings could be completed, the bench changed. The matter was reheard by the new division bench on almost a daily basis for less than a month this year.

news.title: Hubballi: Residents of KHB Colony demand e-khata for their properties
news.para: ​For 15 years, authorities failed to provide e-property documentation, preventing residents from availing loans and completing property transactions.

news.title: Bengaluru civic body sets Rs 5,600 crore property tax target for FY26
news.para: According to officials BBMP plans to collaborate with BESCOM to access data on commercial buildings. Some properties have been misclassified as residential units to pay lower taxes.

news.title: Mysuru civic body to launch three-month drive to issue B-khatas
news.para: An estimated 57,000 properties will be covered under the initiative, which aims to regularise violations and boost property tax collection.

news.title: Mother writes to Lodha brothers to resolve brand dispute as per family agreement
news.para: The wife of Maharashtra cabinet minister Mangal Prabhat Lodha has asked both the sons to respect and not to say anything wrong about each other, not to fight, and not interfere in each other’s businesses.

news.title: Over 25,000 Supertech homebuyers staring at uncertain future
news.para: Homebuyers face further delays as NBCC started the groundwork for completing 16 housing projects, comprising 49,748 homes, in Uttar Pradesh, Uttarakhand, Haryana and Karnataka.
